# Static MVP baseline
#
# No environment variables are required to build or host the current content-only
# MVP. Keep the root environment empty until a feature introduces a documented
# need for configuration.
#
# Guidance:
# - Do not add server-only secrets for static UI work.
# - Only add NEXT_PUBLIC_* variables when the UI truly needs compile-time public
#   configuration.
# - Let Next.js manage NODE_ENV instead of setting it manually here.
